
Install SoGo connector. Can be downloaded from here:
http://www.sogo.nu/fr/downloads/frontends.html
or here:
http://www.sogo.nu/files/downloads/extensions/

Install via addons menu in Thunderbird. The "=" button near the menu should open a sub-menu which
contains a menu item "Install from file".

Add a remote address book based on WebDAV link in Owncloud. You must right click and press
synchronize to fetch contacts.

Install calendar support as mentioned in this link:
http://www.techiecorner.com/176/how-to-add-calendar-in-thunderbird-lightning-calendar-add-ons/

In calendar, add new calender, choose remote/internet calendar. Rest is straight forward.

